111
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,300
Don't be mad.

112
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:23,940
Su Yanli, if you keep this up,
I won't talk to you.

113
00:05:30,380 --> 00:05:32,420
Tell me, what are you upset about?

114
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:35,460
Bai Wushuang,

115
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:37,860
